      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Several win chances. STATS (4) has finished eighth and sixth in two runs this campaign but both over sharper trips. Has a great record this longer journey and won 3/6 when third-up. Looks well weighted and suspect he's ready to fire. BEAU RAIN (3) resumed from a long spell with a solid fifth here fresh. Strong record course and distance and from six second-up runs has two wins and four minors. Another that will improve into this. SWEET KISSES (5) has been freshened since placing in the same race as BEAU RAIN. Another with good course and distance stats and looks well weighted here. TYCOON BEAU (6) split BEAU RAIN and SWEET KISSES two back then was fourth last time on heavy ground. Rates highly on best and can improve with firmer footing. BURRANEER BUOY (7) has been winding up strongly and can run into the finish.",
